	<Title>
		Ankle weights for fitness walkers: Good idea?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		When you walk, skip the ankle weights and simply pick up the pace.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Could ankle weights help me get more out of my usual walking routine?
	</Question>
